Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.54,0:00:11.69,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}I want to shine on you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.96,0:00:15.03,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}And always light the dazzling sun
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.33,0:00:18.52,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}I want to defend you from all the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.85,0:00:23.39,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}This is the truth from my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.61,0:00:34.83,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}心の奥 繋げたら 信じてもらえるのにね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.05,0:00:46.13,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}今見えなくても  失くさないでいて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.51,0:00:54.21,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}その優しさは無駄じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.92,0:00:58.33,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}風に乗って浮かび
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.60,0:01:01.67,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}ここじゃないどこかへ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.00,0:01:05.19,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}海を越え　時を越え
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.47,0:01:08.73,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}きっと咲くだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.98,0:01:15.39,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}いつの日にも　いつもそんな君を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.77,0:01:22.34,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}太陽のようにずっと見守れたらいいな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.75,0:01:30.33,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}This is truth From my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.09,0:23:13.03,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}膝抱え一人涙堪えた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.29,0:23:19.95,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}どうしようもない　不安に負けそうな夜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.42,0:23:25.49,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}気がつけば　いつだってすぐ側に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.79,0:23:32.70,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}他の誰でもなくあなたがいてくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.01,0:23:43.49,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}“強くなりたい”　願い続けてはまた躓いて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.89,0:23:53.51,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}傷つくけど　信じられるあなたがいるから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.76,0:23:56.48,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}立ち上がれるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.76,0:24:08.37,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}「ありがとう」ただ伝えたい　愛しい人へ　声の限り何度だって
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.61,0:24:15.62,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}掛け替えのない私の愛しい人へ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.91,0:24:20.92,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}届いていますか
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.20,0:24:29.20,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}変わりゆく世界　変わらない人のぬくもり
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.43,0:24:32.73,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}確かに感じた
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.03,0:24:39.85,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}愛しい人へ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.09,0:23:13.03,ed_Chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}獨個兒抱著膝忍住了眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.29,0:23:19.95,ed_Chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}快要輸給令人不安、沒希望的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.42,0:23:25.49,ed_Chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}如果注意到　一直不論怎樣也馬上來陪伴我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.79,0:23:32.70,ed_Chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}沒有別的人　卻有你在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.01,0:23:43.49,ed_Chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}一直祈求 “想變得堅強”　結果還是跌交
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.89,0:23:53.51,ed_Chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}雖然受傷　不過相信你在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.76,0:23:56.48,ed_Chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}我就能振作起來喲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.76,0:24:08.37,ed_Chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}只想向你傳達一句「謝謝」 我摯愛的人 多少次 即使知道我的聲音有限
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.61,0:24:15.62,ed_Chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}也要向我那無可替代的摯愛的人呼喊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.91,0:24:20.92,ed_Chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}傳到了你那裡了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.20,0:24:29.20,ed_Chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}變更的世界　沒有變改的人的溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.43,0:24:32.73,ed_Chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}我確實地感覺到了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.03,0:24:39.85,ed_Chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}我摯愛的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.83,0:01:47.36,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接近水源了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.60,0:02:00.82,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,处在那尤古和萨古的夹缝之中了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.43,0:02:24.33,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.97,0:02:29.65,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴尔沙 这些花是我们最后的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.14,0:02:32.28,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能用这个去就查古穆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.99,0:02:35.22,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了 试试看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.65,0:02:38.34,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会保护查古穆的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.31,0:02:41.42,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,药草师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.53,0:02:44.58,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些花对我们也有效吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.79,0:02:47.56,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只要稍微施加一点咒术
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.65,0:02:50.86,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕无论是谁都能触碰到那尤古的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.92,0:02:53.36,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这花也分给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.55,0:02:55.39,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是粉身碎骨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.63,0:02:58.84,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不会让你希望白费的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.36,0:03:01.38,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.96,0:03:04.32,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是想真么拜托你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.98,0:03:07.19,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一定要保护好查古穆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.32,0:03:08.47,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感激
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.49,0:03:21.08,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样吃了就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.60,0:03:34.01,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.43,0:03:36.45,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去查古穆去的那尤古
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.32,0:03:47.78,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.07,0:03:49.42,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.41,0:03:59.37,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经看不见刚才的食卵者了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.15,0:04:05.25,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 什么都看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.03,0:04:08.58,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是西沽花的效果吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.86,0:04:11.18,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定没这么快起效
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.44,0:04:13.59,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是要相信药草师的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.61,0:04:15.89,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之现在追上王子是首要的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.99,0:04:21.03,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们从占星师那里到底得到了什么样的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.12,0:04:22.18,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修加大人说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.37,0:04:25.71,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到紧要关头的时候忘记精灵的卵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.92,0:04:28.73,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之保护王子是最优先的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.05,0:04:30.77,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.77,0:04:32.81,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某种意义上来说是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.49,0:04:35.41,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就赌他这个判断
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.65,0:04:38.92,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算卵被孵化了 但查古穆死了的话就没有意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.71,0:04:46.54,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算止血了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.54,0:05:05.52,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确是生物没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.75,0:05:07.79,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想像不出是这个世界上的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.33,0:05:12.99,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.37,0:05:16.16,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你收到传讯了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.36,0:05:17.22,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.62,0:05:21.46,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后巴尔沙他们朝着萨南去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.69,0:05:23.53,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.53,0:05:26.01,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不亏是托卢卡师所教授的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.07,0:05:29.19,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 比起那个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.28,0:05:33.00,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那个这是什么 这个怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.17,0:05:35.11,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎么打倒的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.35,0:05:37.95,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吃了西沽花
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.29,0:05:40.09,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以花为触媒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.30,0:05:44.18,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也能感触到那尤古的东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.44,0:05:45.92,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.49,0:05:48.23,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好 弟子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.56,0:05:51.50,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个花还有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.50,0:05:55.72,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾 全都给了巴尔沙他们了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.72,0:05:56.74,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.13,0:06:01.33,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的年龄的话还有一次机会能看到精灵的诞生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.57,0:06:04.63,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我却是最后的机会了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.46,0:06:07.77,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是最后一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.31,0:06:09.36,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托卢卡师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.53,0:06:11.53,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.13,0:06:14.25,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之现在要追上王子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.36,0:06:16.52,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别着急
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.61,0:06:18.78,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黎明之前不会被吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.61,0:06:29.68,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.85,0:06:31.27,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只熊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.63,0:06:33.42,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.80,0:06:38.72,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉伦加
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.85,0:06:40.18,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.34,0:06:41.06,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.41,0:07:08.44,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.75,0:07:12.03,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕那是尤佳罗伊穆的卵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.08,0:07:14.94,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然想到了查古穆以外的精灵守护人但是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.13,0:07:20.10,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像那样的被淘汰掉就是大自然的哲理吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.23,0:07:21.88,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 查古穆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.98,0:07:26.82,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 看来黎明之前这段时间也不是安全的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.93,0:07:29.20,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快走吧 占星师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.29,0:07:31.50,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅 也带上我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.77,0:07:33.90,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 让他一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.38,0:07:35.93,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.43,0:07:38.99,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你骑马吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.99,0:08:03.12,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可思议 完全不觉得冷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.73,0:08:12.25,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是萨南
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.40,0:08:21.75,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多要生下来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.72,0:08:45.49,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴尔沙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.55,0:08:48.15,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴尔沙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.51,0:08:51.24,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.93,0:08:55.60,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查古穆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.69,0:08:57.28,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.78,0:09:00.81,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.95,0:09:02.78,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用短枪的 你先去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.04,0:09:03.94,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.07,0:09:05.53,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想办法拦住它
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.32,0:09:38.65,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查古穆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.88,0:09:42.52,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴尔沙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.69,0:09:44.98,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.33,0:09:47.79,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴尔沙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.01,0:09:50.30,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得你一定会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.83,0:09:52.55,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.72,0:09:54.23,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴尔沙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.33,0:10:05.54,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寸 射这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.16,0:10:15.66,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.15,0:10:33.09,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.85,0:10:36.24,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那尤古这里是水里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.29,0:10:38.20,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.32,0:10:42.29,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来这里在那尤古是水里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.41,0:10:45.84,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先到山崖上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.69,0:11:06.99,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干掉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.04,0:11:23.75,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴尔沙 查古穆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.28,0:11:27.47,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到见王子吗 哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.15,0:11:30.83,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 我也看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.96,0:11:33.89,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弟子看得见我看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.34,0:11:35.98,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.11,0:11:40.74,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所了解的世界只是这个世界的一半
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.85,0:11:43.56,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 只有万分之一吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.40,0:11:46.40,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 快点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.39,0:12:00.09,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不能杀死拉伦加
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.04,0:12:03.43,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 查古穆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.92,0:12:05.83,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要出生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.00,0:12:11.34,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然我不被拉伦加撕成碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.45,0:12:13.80,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就出不来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.16,0:12:18.44,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤脑筋 这样我不知道该怎么办才好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.69,0:12:25.88,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅 我先去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.47,0:12:58.06,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.59,0:13:00.79,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头领 箭已经没了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.91,0:13:03.10,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右也没有多少了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.36,0:13:08.11,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传说中的8人武士在这种情况下战斗了三天三夜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.23,0:13:09.41,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使油没有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.53,0:13:13.91,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了那个药草师我们可以和那尤古之物厮杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.05,0:13:15.96,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算豁出性命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.07,0:13:18.47,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这一把剑也要战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.71,0:13:21.54,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像头领说的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.18,0:13:24.74,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不可能做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.13,0:13:29.55,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用短枪的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.76,0:13:32.25,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带王子离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.36,0:13:34.81,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让王子逃走是首要的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.96,0:13:35.58,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.66,0:13:37.34,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查古穆 振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.43,0:13:38.81,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.19,0:13:41.80,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不行 巴尔沙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.41,0:13:44.84,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卵想留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.02,0:13:47.25,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果今天不在这里孵化的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.41,0:13:50.40,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卵就会死在我的体内
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.54,0:13:52.37,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.59,0:13:55.53,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卵想要在这里孵化
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.42,0:13:59.04,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走 用短枪的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.17,0:14:00.39,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.06,0:14:11.25,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.14,0:14:27.89,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴尔沙 我也还想活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.97,0:14:30.77,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我的身体被命运所左右
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.87,0:14:33.59,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无法做到牺牲大家而活
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.73,0:14:37.55,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能牺牲萨古百万百姓的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.66,0:14:41.50,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 不要再战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.61,0:14:45.21,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要做只有我能够做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.47,0:14:47.63,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查古穆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.88,0:14:49.90,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.17,0:14:53.45,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王子 不要管我们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.55,0:14:54.84,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.76,0:14:57.07,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.26,0:15:00.92,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棠鞑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.78,0:15:07.81,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是去了那尤古
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.85,0:15:09.90,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴尔沙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.19,0:15:14.81,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要担心 查古穆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.91,0:15:18.42,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才师傅教了我取出精灵之卵的咒术
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.57,0:15:21.44,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以先要把查古穆代到安全的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.50,0:15:22.73,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.97,0:15:30.69,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 占星师说200年前也用了同样的办法 差一点就成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.22,0:15:32.75,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.81,0:15:34.48,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查古穆拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.78,0:15:39.82,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.97,0:15:42.43,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都不用担心 查古穆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.66,0:16:04.80,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托卢卡师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.00,0:16:08.21,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有我们能做的事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.47,0:16:09.57,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.83,0:16:12.88,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安静的等待黎明的到来并祈祷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.11,0:16:16.43,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查古穆 拜托了 快动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.93,0:16:23.64,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底有多少只
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.38,0:16:25.85,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没完没了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.08,0:16:32.48,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托卢卡师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.57,0:16:38.46,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来在很很多的拉伦加在战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.42,0:16:42.90,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.29,0:16:48.64,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.40,0:17:00.54,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 跟上用短枪的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.34,0:17:30.64,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴尔沙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.73,0:17:57.52,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝日
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.67,0:18:00.98,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 萨古的太阳升起了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.63,0:18:21.37,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.48,0:18:25.61,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.11,0:18:28.26,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴尔沙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.82,0:18:34.91,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.24,0:18:36.64,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.98,0:18:41.13,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快点的话那尤古和萨古会完全分离的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.28,0:18:42.15,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.64,0:18:44.91,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴尔沙 把手借给我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.64,0:18:48.75,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.91,0:18:53.99,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样慢慢的把收伸进去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.60,0:19:03.39,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.44,0:19:07.66,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.80,0:19:10.35,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样接触到卵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.14,0:19:16.40,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.91,0:19:20.11,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.43,0:19:27.11,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.51,0:19:47.73,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是卵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.77,0:19:59.65,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全的生下来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.86,0:20:04.10,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想活下去 想活下去的心愿实现了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.65,0:20:06.90,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.03,0:20:08.65,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棠鞑 巴尔沙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.23,0:20:14.47,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴尔沙 给让看看卵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.18,0:20:18.92,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于出生了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.72,0:20:21.33,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.25,0:20:29.14,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.30,0:20:30.90,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳吉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.20,0:20:37.53,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那个不来的话刚生下来的卵会立刻死掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.89,0:21:08.67,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳吉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.92,0:21:11.20,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳吉来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.18,0:21:14.74,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实是纳吉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.40,0:21:27.49,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没注意到就飞走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.78,0:21:30.47,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 会注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.26,0:21:46.77,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.93,0:21:49.69,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查古穆 该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.02,0:21:53.31,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把卵扔上天空
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.48,0:21:55.72,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳吉就会叼走卵的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.96,0:22:41.87,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在才追上来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.97,0:22:48.61,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这样就可以护送王子回宫了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.99,0:23:01.08,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束了 和命运的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.29,0:24:43.39,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预告
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.52,0:24:46.32,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把卵托付给纳吉的查古穆和巴尔沙
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.54,0:24:48.40,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成一切归来的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.51,0:24:50.76,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待他们的是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.07,0:24:53.69,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终回 启程
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.97,0:24:56.83,CNSUB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会忘记 你的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
